title: Twisted With Sam Tripoli EP 13: Traffic Court Tripoli
description: Tripoli's back ranting and raving about the trials and tribulations of his hectic life!  Tripoli makes a huge announcement about the Naughty Show. Then Sam discusses his incredible fourteen and three record in traffic court, his trip to Vegas for the NBA Summer League, why the rapper Wes Walker should quit rapping and he answers you questions! All of this and more on a new hour of Twisted with Sam Tripoli!
